  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is

        1. To determine whether the Gastrodia and Uncaria Drink is effective in the treatment of
           masked hypertensive patients below 70 years.

        2. To find out the suitable groups for the Gastrodia and Uncaria Drink treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
